  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><span class="geolocation-title"><img src="/media/13069994/walking-in-the-mountains-in-switzerland-with-a-cow.jpg" alt="Save £50 per person on Swiss holidays" data-udi="umb://media/f6cfc7385b14423ca4066dbb4e61cc1b" /></span></p>
<p><span class="geolocation-title">Discover Switzerland with an Inghams Lakes &amp; Mountains holiday in 2019. Book before the 30 September 2018 and save £50 per person on a summer holiday to one of these incredible Swiss hotels: the Hotel Silberhorn in Wengen, the Parkhotel Beau Site in Zermatt, and the Hotel Du Lac in Interlaken.</span></p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="color: #7ea537;">Hotel Silberhorn, Wengen</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13057528/hotel-silberhorn-wengen-bernese-oberland-switzerland-hotel-exterior.jpg" alt="Hotel Silberhorn in Wengen" data-udi="umb://media/65a6584f227d43c08737d0b422e113c2" /></p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3}" title="Wengen"><strong>Wengen</strong> </a>offers visitors an abundance of Alpine trails that meander through pine forests and flower filled fields. The excellent network of mountain railways and cable-cars makes Wengen a perfect base from which to explore the beautiful Jungfrau region.</p>
<p>In the heart of Wengen, the 4* <a data-udi="umb://document/b781f4a530174af2933bd723d0dc1fbe" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b781f4a530174af2933bd723d0dc1fbe}" title="Hotel Silberhorn"><strong>Hotel Silberhorn</strong></a> is only a short walk from the village cable-car and directly opposite the quaint, village train station. The hotel has a fantastic wellness centre with steambath, Jacuzzi and sauna, and provides an excellent choice of food with hot and cold breakfast buffets and 5 course evening meals.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b781f4a530174af2933bd723d0dc1fbe" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b781f4a530174af2933bd723d0dc1fbe}" title="Hotel Silberhorn"><strong>View the Hotel Silberhorn &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="color: #7ea537;">Parkhotel Beau Site, Zermatt</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13058382/parkhotel-beau-site-zermatt-switzerland-terrace.jpg" alt="Parkhotel Beau Site, Zermatt" data-udi="umb://media/7b2d6e6860934e16833ae696c3a3b04e" /></p>
<p>Zermatt’s charming car-free village has plenty of character with amazing walking opportunities. Featuring an excellent mountain transport network, guests can access breath-taking circular panoramic trails and the nearby lakes.</p>
<p>The <a data-udi="umb://document/acb5b34744b74e408ca29b96eb446fd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acb5b34744b74e408ca29b96eb446fd7}" title="Parkhotel Beau Site"><strong>Parkhotel Beau Site</strong></a> has excellent views across <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt"><strong>Zermatt</strong></a>, including towards the iconic Matterhorn mountain. Fantastic facilities include the indoor pool area and an extensive spa, while the hotel serves exceptional cuisine with a hot and cold breakfast buffet and 4 course evening meals.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/acb5b34744b74e408ca29b96eb446fd7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/acb5b34744b74e408ca29b96eb446fd7}" title="Parkhotel Beau Site"><strong>Discover the Parkhotel Beau Site &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="color: #7ea537;">Hotel Du Lac, Interlaken</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13057345/view-of-the-hotel-du-lac-exterior-with-paragliders-up-above.jpg" alt="Hotel Du Lac, Interlaken" data-udi="umb://media/db2fc4d4ff774b6bb5a3741eb344d104" /></p>
<p>Situated between stunning, glacial blue lakes and magnificent, soaring mountains, the town of <a data-udi="umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7456bae57241449a84a68959b62b2aba}" title="Interlaken"><strong>Interlaken</strong> </a>is a bustling but relaxing destination which is ideal for sightseeing and gentle activities in the mountains.</p>
<p>The <a data-udi="umb://document/5bc5e5345df84fd2a80612596bfc0dc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5bc5e5345df84fd2a80612596bfc0dc3}" title="Hotel Du Lac"><strong>Hotel Du Lac</strong></a> has a wonderful riverside location, with easy access to the towns flower lined promenade and the huge open meadow. The train station and ferry terminal are also close by, allowing you to explore all the area’s riches with relative ease.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/5bc5e5345df84fd2a80612596bfc0dc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5bc5e5345df84fd2a80612596bfc0dc3}" title="Hotel Du Lac"><strong>Find out more about the Hotel Du Lac &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="color: #7ea537;">Win a Swiss Hamper worth up to £200</h2>
<p>Enter our competition to win a hamper of Swiss goodies worth up to £200. Prize draw closes on the 30 September 2018, terms and conditions apply.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/be029c32610a4844b409a45c9425b2ed" href="/{localLink:umb://document/be029c32610a4844b409a45c9425b2ed}" title="Swiss Competition"><strong>Enter competition here &gt;</strong></a></p>
</div>]]></bodyText>
